OL,3,CMandatory school uniform items to be
OL,4,Climited to three under new Schools Bill
OL,6,FThe parents of four million children
OL,7,Fwill get cheaper school uniforms
OL,8,Fbecause of a law reform making its way
OL,9,Fthrough Parliament, the Government has
OL,10,Fclaimed.
OL,12,FThe Children's Wellbeing and Schools
OL,13,FBill will reduce uniform costs for
OL,14,Ffamilies by #70 million across
OL,15,FEngland, according to analysis by the
OL,16,FDepartment for Education (DfE).
OL,18,FMPs have previously raised concerns
OL,19,Fabout the high costs parents face in
OL,20,Fbuying branded items of clothing for
OL,21,Funiform.
