OL,3,CMandatory school uniform items to be
OL,4,Climited to three under new Schools Bill
OL,6,FSchools are required to limit the
OL,7,Famount of branded uniform items but a
OL,8,Fsurvey has shown they are not doing
OL,9,Fso, with parents having to pay on
OL,10,Faverage #442 for secondary school
OL,11,Funiforms, and #343 for primary school
OL,12,Funiforms.
OL,14,FAs the House of Lords continues
OL,15,Fscrutiny of the Bill, the Government
OL,16,Fhas insisted it will help to reduce
OL,17,Fthe costs of school uniform by placing
OL,18,Flimits on the number of branded items
OL,19,Fschools can require children to have.
