OL,6,F"Alongside our free breakfast clubs,
OL,7,Fthese new laws will save parents
OL,8,Fhundreds of pounds a year and make
OL,9,Fsure family finances have no bearing
OL,10,Fon children's time at school.
OL,12,F"This Bill is about keeping children
OL,13,Fsafe, saving parents money and
OL,14,Fbringing every school up to the
OL,15,Fstandard of the best, so we can break
OL,16,Fdown barriers to opportunity and
OL,17,Fdeliver our plan for change."
OL,19,FThe new uniform laws will save parents
OL,20,F#50 a year in the back-to-school shop,
OL,21,Faccording to the DfE.
