OL,6,FAlongside the uniform limits, the Bill
OL,7,Fproposes to introduce free breakfast
OL,8,Fclubs, create a new register of all
OL,9,Fhome-schooled children in England and
OL,10,Freform academies.
OL,12,FMinisters have faced criticism from
OL,13,Fadvocates for the academy system for
OL,14,Fmoves they believe will restrict their
OL,15,Ffreedoms and which could limit their
OL,16,Fpay scales.
